Turns out it was bottleneck

@jreback right now `bn_ok_dtype` excludes datetime & timedelta, but not datetimetz in https://github.com/pandas-dev/pandas/blob/19f715c51d16995fc6cd0c102fdba2f213a83a0f/pandas/core/nanops.py#L147

I assume we don't want to pass datetimetz to bottleneck, since the actual operation should be done on the same values (i8 or M8[ns]).
